Class RTSI

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sat4j.sat.RTSI

  • public class RTSI
extends Object
    This class allows dynamic search for classes. That code appeared in Java World 113 in an article written by Daniel Le Berre http://www.javaworld.com/javatips/jw-javatip113.html The initial code of JWhich, on which is based this code, was published in JavaWorld 105 by Mike Clark http://www.javaworld.com/javaworld/javatips/jw-javatip105.html
    Author:
    sroussel and dleberre
